N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 441.64 - Clearing account

State Regulations
A primary account containing costs that are to be
transferred to other accounts; an intermediate account to which is transferred
a group of costs or revenues or a group of accounts containing costs or
revenues and from which a distribution of the total is made to other
accounts. Notes
